<h2 id="indexing-a-dictionary-of-graphs">Indexing a dictionary of graphs</h2>

<p>Given these ops you could imagine a dictionary of graphs.</p>

\[\{v_i: g_i \mid\;\text{where}\; v_i = f(g_i) \} \\\]

<p>This dictionary can be indexed by a graph.</p>

